Primary school to shut due to gas supply issues
Updated 10:23am Tuesday 3rd May 2016 in
DROVE Primary School has announced it will be closing today due to gas supply issues.
Parents are currently being informed of closure.
More details to follow.
Due to a disruption with our gas supply, the school will now be closing at 10:30am today. Parents please check text for more details.
Drove Primary School (@DrovePriSchool) May 3, 2016
